[[gulf|Gulf]] of [[Thailand]]




==English==



===Noun===



1.An [[inland]] body of [[water]] in the [[Pacific Ocean]] that is [[southeast]] of [[Southeast Asia]] below the [[country|countries]] of [[Myanmar]],[[Thailand]],and [[Cambodia]],and is close to the [[Malay Peninsula]] of [[Malaysia]].


